{"tid":1574604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大連儂牆出現多張「天滅中共」、「全黨死清光」海報","createTime":"2019-09-16T13:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:21:53.000Z","uid":37112,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b65f91d2c63a604268176c4ccc852a7a04da2c9","tid":1574604,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2589497897780028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2589497897780028&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=0fa5ce06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2589497897780028</a><br />\n<br />\n【港大連儂牆】<br />\n<br />\n香港大學連儂牆及學生會大樓外牆被貼上「天滅中共」、「全黨死清光」、「God Damn Beijing 」等字眼的海報，又有批評校長張翔的標語。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mad0o3S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMad0o3S.png&h=e2c27313&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmCXrhe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmCXrhe.png&h=321a6907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sB3SZCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsB3SZCf.png&h=bebad116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07ed371454375d72c8e9a76b257950edb0aae271","tid":1574604,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自